FBIS4-40940 "drsov119_b_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Announces New Government Appointments Yeltsin Announces New Government Appointments LD2006164594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1603 GMT 20 Jun 94 LD2006164594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow June 20 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin signed several decrees on Monday appointing Aleksey Kazakov head of the Department for Work with Territories of the Russian Presidential Administration and Vladimir Varov head of the Federal Labour Inspectorate of the Russian Ministry of Labour, Chief Labour Inspector. Yeltsin also appointed Vladimir Zaitsev first deputy head of the Russian President's Auditing Department and put him in charge of the department, the presidential press service said.
